reviewText:
I'm 20 years old. I watched this with my friends at college. It was the best night of our lives.

I recommend this to people of any age who want to have a good time. PERIOD.

I'm head over heals for catchy christmas jingles, and older babies.  This is entertaining for the whole family, your baby will even giggle and gawk as it stares at his/her contemporaries. A must.
I was first introduced to the series by the original Jingle Cats L.P. and immediately caught the fever. Some of my friends are at first charmed by the general witt, and then, after several listenings, or watchings, they began to appreciate the musicianship showcased.
Great at parties!!!!!
This film just changed our toddler's cries to smiles and happiness. JUST AMAZING.
